| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0293 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 72658d40-81e4-5056-97e5-50da1a63d42b"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
